last_episode_to_air.overview: Anne gets a wake-up call. Rose's life changes. Bo asks for another chance. Nina fights back. Dicte crosses a moral boundary to stop Maj's stalker.

name: Dicte
overview: Newly divorced journalist returns to her hometown to restart her life and work through her past.

episodes.name: Personal (1)
episodes.overview: Part 1: Dicte finds the body of a young woman who died of a C-section. Due to this macabre find, Dicte gets to know Inspector Wagner.

episodes.name: Personal (2)
episodes.overview: Part 2: Dicte finds the body of a young woman who died of a C-section. Due to this macabre find, Dicte gets to know Inspector Wagner.

episodes.name: Deductible (1)
episodes.overview: Part 1: One summer night, Dicte sees a burning cart in the driveway of her neighbors. Inside the house, Inger Gravgård seems to have committed suicide.

episodes.name: Deductible (2)
episodes.overview: Part 2: One summer night, Dicte sees a burning cart in the driveway of her neighbors. Inside the house, Inger Gravgård seems to have committed suicide.

episodes.name: Hidden Defects (1)
episodes.overview: Part 1: A bath tub with the corpse of a newborn floats in the harbor. Dicte goes with her gut but Wagner warns her not to jump to conclusions.

episodes.name: Hidden Defects (2)
episodes.overview: Part 2: A bath tub with the corpse of a newborn floats in the harbor. Dicte goes with her gut but Wagner warns her not to jump to conclusions.

episodes.name: Life and Body (1)
episodes.overview: Dicte follows a tip about illegal organ trafficking related to the murder of a young man. She later finds herself face to face with someone from her past.

episodes.name: Life and Body (2)
episodes.overview: Dicte and Wagner find themselves on the trail of the same man. And Dicte finds herself in a personal dilemma. Bo and Dicte become closer than ever before.

episodes.name: Violence and Power (1)
episodes.overview: After Dicte finishes an interview with prominent politician, Francesca Olsen, a bomb explodes nearby. The explosion kills a young woman, but Dicte is convinced that the actual target was Francesca.

episodes.name: Violence and Power (2)
episodes.overview: Dicte fights to prove the innocence of her biological son, Peter, but she soon discovers more about him than she had bargained for.

episodes.name: Dreams and Diamonds (1)
episodes.overview: After years with no contact to her parents, Dicte's father approaches her from out of the blue. Meanwhile, a young black woman is found murdered at a nearby hotel.

episodes.name: Dreams and Diamonds (2)
episodes.overview: Dicte and Wagner are lead into the world of prostitution and a mysterious woman helps them apprehend the killer. Dicte and Bo meet Rose's new boyfriend.

episodes.name: Passion and Handcuffs (1)
episodes.overview: The local wellness queen is found dead in what looks like a sex-game gone wrong. Dicte deals with Rose wanting to leave home and accidentally comes between Torsten and Anne.

episodes.name: Passion and Handcuffs (2)
episodes.overview: Dicte and Wagner realize they have apprehended the wrong perpetrator and the hunt for the killer continues. Things get more serious between Bo and Dicte, and Wagner is oblivious to an office romance happening right in front of him.

episodes.name: Closeness and Distance (1)
episodes.overview: The little sister of Rose's friend disappears at a party. Dicte fights for Wagner to take the matter seriously. Dicte visits her father in the hospital.

episodes.name: Closeness and Distance (2)
episodes.overview: Wagner and Dicte continue the search for the missing girl and start chasing a suspect using the social media to groom young girls. Bo moves in with Dicte.

episodes.name: Means and Ends (1)
episodes.overview: After the death of a football player Dicte finds herself digging into the world of hooliganism and contract players. Torsten and Anne have broken up and Rose gets to know her grandmother.

episodes.name: Means and Ends (2)
episodes.overview: Wagner and Dicte have found evidence of match fixing, but it also looks like Rose's boyfriend might be involved. Rose and Dicte fight over Rose's contact with her grandmother.

episodes.name: Right and Responsibility (1)
episodes.overview: Wagner's affair with a beautiful black woman has serious consequences when she is found dead, and the investigator is suspended.

episodes.name: Right and Responsibility (2)
episodes.overview: Dicte and Wagner break all rules in order to solve the murder of Grace and clear Wagner's name. Dicte tries to make peace with Rose and perhaps also her mother.

episodes.name: After the wedding (part 1)
episodes.overview: Bo and Dicte are getting married. The day after the wedding Bo is going on a journalist assignment to Lebanon and is taken as hostage.

episodes.name: After the wedding (part 2)
episodes.overview: Dicte goes to identify the body brought back from Lebanon. Turns out she will still need the ransom.

episodes.name: In Wagner's footsteps (part 1)
episodes.overview: Dicte's grief compels her to take care of some unfinished business: the investigation of a missing mother who disappeared after attending a party.

episodes.name: In Wagner's footsteps (part 2)
episodes.overview: A found suitcase suggests a suspect other then Tina's husband. A photo calls into question the story of Johan and Bo's escape attempt in Syria.

episodes.name: Illness of the mind (part 1)
episodes.overview: At Rose's new job, a young psych patient makes a startling observation about her and is later found dead. Dicte's relationship woes come to ahead.

episodes.name: Illness of the mind (part 2)
episodes.overview: The victims' DIS similarities lead police to suspect the murders were mercy killings. Rose gets some surprising news. Dicte makes a decision about Bo.

episodes.name: The price of addiction (part 1)
episodes.overview: Police investigate a copycat heist of an amusement park's safe. Rose breaks the news to her lover. Anne struggles with the demands of her new job.

episodes.name: The price of addiction (part 2)
episodes.overview: The police suspect the kidnapper is a gambling addict. Rumors about Nena spread. Victor agrees to go undercover in a casino but gets in over her head.

episodes.name: Every man is an island (part 1)
episodes.overview: Dicte learns her father lied to her. A young single mom claims she's being stalked, but Dicte isn't sure she believes her. Nina is sexually harassed.

episodes.name: Every man is an island (part 2)
episodes.overview: Anne gets a wake-up call. Rose's life changes. Bo asks for another chance. Nina fights back. Dicte crosses a moral boundary to stop Maj's stalker.
